OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with rain, persistent at
OL,6,Ftimes. This turns to patchy drizzle as
OL,7,Fbright spells develop later in the
OL,8,Fmorning. Many places become dry with
OL,9,Fbright or sunny spells as the drizzle
OL,10,Fclears to the occasional shower from
OL,11,Fthe early afternoon.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FThe evening will see bright
OL,14,Fspells with the occasional shower.
OL,15,FThese showers will die later with
OL,16,Fcloud and patchy drizzle following
OL,17,Feast from midnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
