OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FLow cloud and drizzle will
OL,6,Fclear for a time in the morning.
OL,7,FFurther cloud and rain will push north
OL,8,Fduring the afternoon.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FOutbreaks
OL,11,Fof locally heavy rain spread northeast
OL,12,FFriday. This clears to sunny spells
OL,13,Fand the odd shower Saturday. Orkney
OL,14,Fwill become dry as the odd shower
OL,15,Fcontinues over Shetland Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
